{"tid":875760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女兒哭訴被性騷擾 父15秒怒出22拳打爆淫師","createTime":"2018-10-25T06:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T11:39:19.000Z","uid":75969,"like":71,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"f6e321b4ac19bd128421045f3ce41a35a2dbcce1","tid":875760,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T06:10:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181025/_2018102511450777975.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181025%2F_2018102511450777975.jpg&h=2e078ed5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">懷疑性騷擾女學生的老師被少女父親暴打，滿臉是傷。（網圖）</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿根廷一名15歲少女向父親哭訴遭學校老師性騷擾，父親帶她到學校去理論，結果該名父親即時火遮眼，一看到懷疑性騷擾女兒的老師就衝向對方在15秒內打出22拳將對方打爆，該名老師的臉被揍得滿是傷，網民都說大快人心，可是以暴力解決問題還是不當啊！<br />\n<br />\n在阿根廷中部聖瑪爾塔（Santa Marta）商業女校擔任教師的30歲男子克魯賽諾（Jorge Cruceno），日前被一名15歲的女學生指控透過手機短訊進行性騷擾。女學生的父親在手機上發現許多猥褻內容，便即時跑到學校找校方理論，可是剛到校園就遇到淫師克魯賽諾，盛怒之下衝上去將其打了一頓。<br />\n<br />\n影片中可看到，穿着黑衣的父親，一看到克魯賽諾就立即飛撲過去，二話不說就是一拳，更在15秒連續打了22拳，當場將克魯賽諾打爆。<br />\n<br />\n克魯賽諾的頭部縫了多針，臉上也有多處瘀傷，克魯賽諾事後前往警局報案，反告少女父親。警方正在調查雙方糾紛，至於性騷擾案也同時在調查中。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20181025/_2018102511450535038.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20181025%2F_2018102511450535038.jpg&h=2fcdd637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">該名老師受傷前的樣貌。（網圖）<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/848557\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F848557&d=w%2BUZzSIMS1FTQuacT6qlJ7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=2e0a77d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F848557&h=7938284e\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/848557</a><br />\n<br />\n打完仲型咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3060bb077dc0ed073956f9a8de8def6e65f5ae2","tid":875760,"uid":36791,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T06:12:27.000Z","msg":"還原靚靚拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c48b064a19a9809c8691daaf6f4b5d29eb35ae9","tid":875760,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T06:15:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">快<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"1eaea385a32cb7505d1ea7718d48d882d2b3aeb0","tid":875760,"uid":3549,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T06:19:07.000Z","msg":"隻手落左gel打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74384355713e5dc1bc304836d553512840c87442","tid":875760,"uid":105059,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T06:20:22.000Z","msg":"拳風勁到可以gel頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85270c63910f951fe49b6b6c02308137a952ff87","tid":875760,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T06:21:41.000Z","msg":"身體接觸性騷擾打佢都合理<br />\n手機騷擾捉佢就算"},{"pid":"949a330855472dfd01e4e600bcc30273745a6a27","tid":875760,"uid":90244,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T06:22:21.000Z","msg":"完美演繹咩叫怒髮沖冠"},{"pid":"661573117b6e330331b002da61ac40f13e4a398e","tid":875760,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T06:24:13.000Z","msg":"哇打打打打打⋯"},{"pid":"91a05ca9246e263c0ebd55e595f6ae30d8d4b4fe","tid":875760,"uid":90890,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T06:24:58.000Z","msg":"俾人打完靚仔左咁多嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hk